                <p class="text-gray-700">At Sohan Soft Tech, we use cookies and similar technologies to improve your browsing experience, analyze website traffic, and personalize our services. This Cookie Policy explains what cookies are, how we use them, and your choices regarding cookies.</p>

                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">1. What Are Cookies?</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">Cookies are small text files placed on your device (computer, tablet, or smartphone) when you visit a website. They allow websites to recognize your device, remember your preferences, and enhance your user experience.</p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">2. Types of Cookies We Use</h4>
                    
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div>
                            <h5 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Essential Cookies</h5>
                            <p class="text-gray-700">These cookies are necessary for the website to function (e.g., login, security, checkout, payment processing).</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div>
                            <h5 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Performance & Analytics Cookies</h5>
                            <p class="text-gray-700">These cookies collect anonymous data about how visitors use our website (pages visited, time spent, errors encountered) to help us improve performance.</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div>
                            <h5 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Functional Cookies</h5>
                            <p class="text-gray-700">These remember your preferences, such as language, region, or login details, to provide a more personalized experience.</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div>
                            <h5 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Advertising & Marketing Cookies</h5>
                            <p class="text-gray-700">We may use these cookies (including third-party cookies like Google or Meta) to deliver relevant ads and measure the effectiveness of our campaigns.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">3. Third-Party Cookies</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">Some cookies may be set by third-party providers such as analytics tools, payment processors (e.g., Razorpay), or embedded services. These third parties may use cookies to deliver their services in compliance with their own privacy policies.</p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">4. Managing Cookies</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">You can manage or disable cookies through your browser settings. Please note that disabling cookies may limit certain features of our website.</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">For more details, check your browser's help pages:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
