                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">3. Lawful Basis for Processing</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">We process personal data only where we have a valid legal basis:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                        <li><strong>Consent</strong> ‚Äì when you voluntarily provide data (e.g., newsletter signup).</li>
                        <li><strong>Contract</strong> ‚Äì to perform services you have requested.</li>
                        <li><strong>Legal Obligation</strong> ‚Äì to comply with tax, regulatory, or legal requirements.</li>
                        <li><strong>Legitimate Interest</strong> ‚Äì to improve our services, ensure security, and prevent fraud.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">4. Data Subject Rights</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">Under GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                        <li>Access the personal data we hold about you.</li>
                        <li>Request correction or deletion of your data.</li>
                        <li>Restrict or object to processing.</li>
                        <li>Request data portability (transfer of your data).</li>
                        <li>Withdraw consent at any time.</li>
                        <li>Lodge a complaint with your local Data Protection Authority.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mt-3">Requests can be made by contacting us at <a href="mailto:info@sohansoft.tech" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">info@sohansoft.tech</a>.</p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">5. Data Retention</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">We retain personal data only as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy, unless a longer retention period is legally required.</p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">6. International Transfers</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">As we operate from India, your data may be transferred outside the EU/EEA. In such cases, we ensure appropriate safeguards (such as encryption, secure storage, and GDPR-compliant third-party processors) are in place.</p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">7. Data Security</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">We apply technical and organizational measures (encryption, access controls, secure servers) to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, or loss.</p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">8. Third-Party Processors</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">We may share data with trusted third-party providers (payment gateways, hosting, analytics tools) strictly under GDPR-compliant agreements and only as necessary to deliver our services.</p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">9. Updates to This Policy</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">We may update this GDPR Policy from time to time. Any updates will be published on this page with the revised "Last Updated" date.</p>
